WEBVTT

00:00:02.760 --> 00:00:06.320
'Tersedak!  Apakah kamu tahu di
mana temanmu Manan berada?'

00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:12.000
'Mama!'

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:13.880
'Manan!'

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:16.800
'Manan!'

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:24.880
